content:
Hello all! This stream will be used for questions and discussions related to the MIT Categories Seminar talks. Ask questions during the live streaming of talks here!
Please keep the discussion on-topic. General information on the MIT category seminar can be found here: http://brendanfong.com/seminar.html .

The Youtube playlist of the talks is here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLhgq-BqyZ7i6Vh4nxlyhKDAMhlv1oWl5n
This includes the upcoming talks as well.
Hey all. Here is the Google Calendar of the seminar: https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=fiadgnrrirqgjqe55r6q447mfc%40group.calendar.google.com&ctz=America%2FToronto
Would it be possible to have the iCal subscription link for the calendar?
